{"tid":2224013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我幫老闆爭取社會資源請殘疾打工，算唔算係為弱勢社群作出貢獻呢？","createTime":"2020-09-30T08:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:45:18.000Z","uid":378580,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a816b4e3298948007594b59f1b5b44877480a4d7","tid":2224013,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"你哋好！我係一個殘疾人士(精神病康復者)，不過我經勞工處展能就業科遇到一個肯請我同已經知道我是殘疾嘅僱主。<br />\n<br />\n這個僱主是一間電腦電話銷售公司，公司全體上下都是殘疾人士，公司亦有申請開政府資助招聘殘疾僱員，當中包括抗疫保就業計劃、就業展才能計劃等，而我是行政職員之一，其中一項工作就是協助公司從社會（包括政府及非政府機構）爭取資助或資源去繼續聘請殘疾僱員。<br />\n<br />\n我公司在殘疾人士請病假的政策上非常尊重，無論請幾少日，只要能只少提供到診紙或病假紙都可獲得有薪病假，對殘疾僱員相當體恤。<br />\n（由於我十月六日開始讀法律證書課程，所以僱主讓我可以一星期五天工作，每日工作六小時，而且只是由下午開始工作，最遲夜晚八點收工，但講好可以提早收工去上堂，現在月薪一個月七千）。<br />\n<br />\n我這一兩天就為了接受覆診和接受腦檢查請了兩日假，途中接過了單張話有間機構只要有僱主肯請殘疾人士工作就願意向佢哋提供最多三個月工資津貼，每個月最高六千元，心諗正啱公司及殘疾僱員需要，即照俾老闆睇，結果佢都感興趣，叫我去了解多啲詳情。<br />\n<br />\n至於張單張俾埋你哋睇，不妨俾下意見，我只求為殘疾界爭取福利保障，做多啲貢獻，如有你的支持或其他意見，我會非常感謝。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5Ac9tN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5Ac9tN.jpg&h=0fadc12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，請聯署為香港人鋪後路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/usa-government-and-congress-should-agree-rent-out-land-democracy-human-right-justice-hker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fusa-government-and-congress-should-agree-rent-out-land-democracy-human-right-justice-hker&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kytVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=5d84d667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/usa-government-and-congress-should-agree-rent-out-land-democracy-human-right-justice-hker</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/552828/sponsors/new?token=U8DuK2JaJIcRVCEG28bT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F552828%2Fsponsors%2Fnew%3Ftoken%3DU8DuK2JaJIcRVCEG28bT&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kytVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b96bad70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/552828/sponsors/new?token=U8DuK2JaJIcRVCEG28bT</a>"},{"pid":"57ee60f623625bb61e474dd66d9091041e2b7d4b","tid":2224013,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"連登真係有白卡佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 支持<br />\n<br />\n利申以前做匡智"},{"pid":"923bdf4a19662dcdc266525539493730c1c4059a","tid":2224013,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058c4a25a9e5052686ced7a07f65d21bfd9d4fc9","tid":2224013,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"有人話殘疾權利係一種特權，我就話係一種補償，各位點睇？"},{"pid":"7d1a7f59e6c0bb3d2c5d94adc70cf17e90666fe6","tid":2224013,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ee60f623625bb61e474dd66d9091041e2b7d4b","tid":2224013,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"連登真係有白卡佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 支持<br />\n<br />\n利申以前做匡智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"匡智是照顧智障的，其實精神病與智障有分別，好多人分唔清楚"},{"pid":"5843bf8bded5dd2b14bedc9c3d83b6997acea29d","tid":2224013,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"殘疾人士需要你們的支持和鼓勵，請回覆和支持更多，我需要集氣和正能量"},{"pid":"583b747976239ff70d63f95132a8969b4c85db3c","tid":2224013,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d1a7f59e6c0bb3d2c5d94adc70cf17e90666fe6","tid":2224013,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ee60f623625bb61e474dd66d9091041e2b7d4b","tid":2224013,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"連登真係有白卡佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/